
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Ideation Phase - Brainstorm & Idea Prioritization</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Ideation Phase - Brainstorm & Idea Prioritization</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Step-1: Select the Problem Statement</h2>
    <p>We selected <b>PS-1 (sterile vintage buyer experience)</b> and <b>PS-2 (high-friction inventory seller tracking)</b> as our core challenges to resolve.</p>

    <h2>Step-2: Brainstorm, Idea Listing & Grouping</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Category</th><th>Brainstormed Ideas</th><th>Technology Blocks</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>UI Aesthetics</b></td>
            <td>Design a warm, pleasant vintage console layout with ivory backgrounds, thick borders, and monospaced font details.</td>
            <td>CSS Custom Variables, Courier Prime / Space Mono Google Fonts, Neubrutalist shadows.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Gamified Checkout</b></td>
            <td>Implement a virtual credit card gateway that visually flips around on CVV focus and loads a secure terminal simulator.</td>
            <td>CSS 3D Transform perspectives, Javascript event hooks, stateful React panels.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Seller Inventory Tracking</b></td>
            <td>Provide a clean console containing key metric indicators, visual progress alerts for stock, and quick status controls.</td>
            <td>Express Seller API, Mongoose aggregation pipelines, Bootstrap UI components.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Step-3: Idea Prioritization (Action Matrix)</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Impact / Effort</th><th>High Priority (Do Now)</th><th>Low Priority (Do Later)</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>High Impact</b></td>
            <td>
                - Cozy sepia console theme styling.<br>
                - Live credit card flipping checkout widget.<br>
                - Seller statistics and low-stock alerts.
            </td>
            <td>
                - Real-time chat with support officers.<br>
                - Automated tax invoice emailing.
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Low Impact</b></td>
            <td>
                - Add multiple filter presets.
            </td>
            <td>
                - Integrated custom background music player.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    